tool_description: Rugby fixtures, results, standings and live match coverage from around the world.
title: Rugby Live Data

api_list.name: Fixtures and Results By Team
api_list.description: All fixtures and results for a given team
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://rugby-live-data.p.rapidapi.com/fixtures-results-by-team/{team_id}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "rugby-live-data.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())

meta.description: Detailed match data for Crusaders v Highlanders - Super Rugby Aotearoa, 2020

events_array.player_1_name: String - For Penalty Tries, value = No Player
events_array.player_2_id: Integer - only visible if type = Substitution
events_array.player_2_name: String - only visible if type = Substitution
events_array.type: String - Try, Penalty Try, Conversion, Penalty, Drop Goal, Missed Drop Goal, Substitution

stat_array.value: String - could be number, string, or double (representing a percentage)

team_stats.stat_name: String - attack, defence, discipline, kicking, breakdown, lineouts, scrums, possession

match.status: String - Not Started, First Half, Half Time, Second Half, Full Time, Result, Postponed, Cancelled

meta.title: Live Rugby API - Match Feed

api_list.name: Fixtures By Team
api_list.description:
Lists only upcoming/in play fixtures for a given team. 

**Note** it will not list any results, so when a match reaches result status it drops off. Use Fixtures and Results By Team OR Fixtures  And Results by Team by Season endpoint for this functionality.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://rugby-live-data.p.rapidapi.com/fixtures-by-team/{team_id}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "rugby-live-data.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())

meta.description: Fixtures and results for given team across all competitions

fields.id: Integer - unique fixture id, use to query match endpoint
fields.status: String - Not Started, First Half, Half Time, Second Half, Full Time, Postponed, Cancelled, Result

meta.title: Live Rugby API -  Upcoming Fixtures for Newport Gwent Dragons
